local,12,0,0.,0.,0.,0.,0.,0.
csys,0
CMBLOCK,_CM28_1 ,ELEM,        4
(8i10)
       781      2467      3404     13400
CMBLOCK,_CM28_2 ,ELEM,       11
(8i10)
       783      2009      2217      2218      2272      7737      7751     13422
     15170     15229     15428
